  "title": "Freelance Social Media Marketing Executive",
  "description": "<p></p><p>Role<br />Own the company’s social media execution end to end on a freelance basis. Content, ads, and on-ground capture. This is a hands-on delivery role, not a strategy-only seat.</p><p>Key Responsibilities<br />Plan and manage weekly social media content across Instagram, Facebook, and TikTok.<br />Create short-form videos. Reels, Shorts, performance-led edits.<br />Shoot photos and videos during classes. On-site presence required on Saturdays.<br />Write clear, parent-facing captions aligned with the brand voice.<br />Set up, run, and optimise Meta ads for enrolment and trial class leads.<br />Track results weekly. Adjust content and ads based on performance data.<br />Coordinate with programme and operations teams around term launches and key campaigns.</p><p>Engagement Terms<br />Freelance contract role. Monthly retainer or per-project basis.</p><p>Requirements<br />Proven experience managing social media accounts for education, enrichment, or family-focused brands.<br />Hands-on experience running paid ads.<br />Strong video shooting and editing skills. Phone and basic gear mastery expected.<br />Comfortable working with children and in live class environments.<br />Reliable availability on weekends.<br />Organised. Self-directed. Deadline-driven.<br />Portfolio required. Social accounts, videos, ad results.</p>",
  "minimumYearsExperience": 2,
